_sText:
Deathrun:

1-3 terrorists
rest CT'S

The point for terrorists is to KILL ct's through traps.
If you can handle all the traps as a ct and come to the end. You get a weapon and can shoot terrorists.

I made some changes from the standard deathrun maps.
--------------------------------
Every counter terrorist start with a smokegrenade. This is funnier!

When you come to the end of the map you can pick between KNIVES and NO KNIVES
Knives: You and the terrorists get teleported to a floor. Knife duel.
No Knives: The door open and you can get weapons to kill them.

Have Fun!
